    <entry>
      <title>欢迎来到敲码小站</title>
      <link href="/2026/07/10/welcome/"/>
      <url>/2026/07/10/welcome/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这是「敲码小站」的第一篇文章。本站使用 <strong>Hexo + Matery</strong> 搭建，并部署到 <strong>GitHub Pages</strong>。</p><h2 id="本站能做什么"><a href="#本站能做什么" class="headerlink" title="本站能做什么"></a>本站能做什么</h2><ul><li>用 Markdown 写技术笔记</li><li>分类、标签、归档</li><li>代码高亮与搜索</li><li>免费托管在 <code>https://你的用户名.github.io</code></li></ul><h2 id="代码示例"><a href="#代码示例" class="headerlink" title="代码示例"></a>代码示例</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">hello</span>():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Hello, 敲码小站!&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">&quot;__main__&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    hello()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="如何写新文章"><a href="#如何写新文章" class="headerlink" title="如何写新文章"></a>如何写新文章</h2><p>在项目根目录执行：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new <span class="string">&quot;文章标题&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后编辑 <code>source/_posts/</code> 下生成的 Markdown 文件，保存后执行：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>即可生成并部署到 GitHub Pages。</p><blockquote><p>坚持写作，持续进步。</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
